[h2 id=GlitchTrickUsed 
	"Glitch/Trick Used
	$LF
]h2
[ul 
	[li 
		"When Mario falls down barely touching the the bottom left corner of the upside down pipes, the scrolling stops and Mario's X-Pos increases.
		$LF
		[ul 
			[li 
				"This was used because when touching the pole normally, the game kind of softlocks or crashes. {
				[a href=https://youtu.be/J5197KA9EqU rel=noopener external nofollow 
					"https://youtu.be/J5197KA9EqU
				]a
				"} I used this Glitch to reach the X-Position that could create a SoftLock situation like in the original game so that player gets down(die) and there it completes.
				$LF
			]li
			[li 
				"Also because normal TAS is LAME !
				$LF
			]li
		]ul
	]li
]ul
[ul 
	[li 
		"We can also live below the screen for a while.
		$LF
	]li
]ul
